the girl from san lorenzo is a 1950 american western film directed by lesley selander and written by adele buffington . the film stars ricardo cortez , coleen gray , peggy stewart , ricardo cortez , peggy stewart , ricardo cortez , peggy stewart , ricardo cortez , peggy stewart , ricardo cortez , peggy stewart , ricardo cortez , peggy stewart , ricardo cortez , harry carey , and cesar romero . the film was released on june 16 , 1950 , by republic pictures .